title: Sportscene - 17th August 2014
description:
Sportscene
17th August 2014 

Highlights of the weekend's action across the SPFL. In the Premiership, Celtic took on Dundee United at home, while Partick Thistle travelled to face Dundee and Kilmarnock played Ross County in Dingwall. Plus highlights of the Edinburgh derby earlier today, and Friday's meeting between Falkirk and Rangers at the Falkirk Stadium in the Championship.
